gov.nih.nci.cabig.caaers.domain.report
Class ReportDefinition

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nci.cabig.ctms.domain.AbstractMutableDomainObject
      gov.nih.nci.cabig.caaers.domain.report.ReportDefinition
All Implemented Interfaces:
gov.nih.nci.cabig.ctms.domain.DomainObject, gov.nih.nci.cabig.ctms.domain.GridIdentifiable, gov.nih.nci.cabig.ctms.domain.MutableDomainObject, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ReportDefinition>
public class ReportDefinition
extends gov.nih.nci.cabig.ctms.domain.AbstractMutableDomainObject
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ReportDefinition>

ReportDefinition represents the predefined set of notifications PlannedNotification objects for an AdverseEventReport. A ReportDefinition is applied or used by the Report to determine the notifications that are to be send out on a particular instance of time. A ReportDefinition instance to be used, is picked-up by the Rules Engine Component, for a specific kind of report based on the name.

Author:
Biju Joseph
